import { TextField } from "@mui/material"
import { Link } from "react-router-dom"

export const Login = () => {

    const login = (e) => {

    }

    return <>
        <form onSubmit={(e) => login(e)}>
            <TextField id="tzInput" label="identity" variant="outlined" va  error={value=="ppp"} required />
            <TextField id="telInput" type="tel" label="phone" variant="outlined" />

        </form>
    </>
}
